{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "TCC Back API",
    "description": "API Express em `/api` (`src/server.ts`). Variáveis da coleção: `protocol`, `host`, `port` (local padrão **http** + **localhost** + **3333**). Para HTTPS sem porta (ex.: Vercel), deixe `port` vazio e use `protocol` **https**.\n\n**URLs (local padrão)**\n| Método | URL |\n|--------|-----|\n| POST | `http://localhost:3333/api/auth` |\n| POST | `http://localhost:3333/api/create` |\n| GET | `http://localhost:3333/api/get-pacients` |\n| POST | `http://localhost:3333/api/create-evolution` |\n| GET | `http://localhost:3333/api/get-evolution` |\n| POST | `http://localhost:3333/api/create-report` |\n| GET | `http://localhost:3333/api/get-report` |\n| PUT | `http://localhost:3333/api/update-report` |\n\n**Auth:** `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`. Login e Create user salvam o `token` na coleção.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "protocol",
      "value": "http"
    },
    {
      "key": "host",
      "value": "localhost"
    },
    {
      "key": "port",
      "value": "3333"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  try {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (data.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', data.token); }",
                  "  } catch (e) { console.warn(e); }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"usuario@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"sua_senha\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{protocol}}://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/auth",
              "protocol": "{{protocol}}",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{port}}",
              "path": ["api", "auth"]
            },
            "description": "URL: `POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/auth`\n\nO campo `username` é o **email** no banco. Resposta: `{ user, token }`."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
